						<h1>病毒亂噴！疾管局調查：一半台灣人咳嗽不戴口罩　趴趴走</h1>

						
						<div id="reporter_info">
														
						<a href="/home/coraline/Documents/Corpus/readability/corpus/zh/html/20120112_www.nownews.com_eb45d1946b6c142b49ee085e191d2fe389bbd6d71ffe5e55bd88c8eb" target="_blank">
